f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebaa9f7319bb9e784cbe7b16261678dd4c43f8f","tid":1659114,"uid":118787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"推，十分認同，一開始真係好想係陳同學件案查出真相，不斷猜測推敲，但大家要冷靜理智返落黎，警方放出嚟既證據cctv，唔會咁容易俾你發現證據，佢地有好專業既團隊去做依件事，所謂漏洞好有可能係引導你地將焦點集中係一件事上，好容易俾有心人帶方向，忽略好多其他同樣重要既事，話會公開俾人雞姦個男仔去咗邊？"},{"pid":"7b20039293d986c612edfd28d7422a5361067cf7","tid":1659114,"uid":294080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:26:02.000Z","msg":"今日又唧牙膏喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黨媒東張西望x受害人媽媽<br />\n引哂去話啊媽係假啊、跟稿讀之類啦"},{"pid":"4578253b017ddd543688d417dac99035d9ffa84f","tid":1659114,"uid":294080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:27:02.000Z","msg":"人地有計劃逐日唧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地中哂計逐日屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e2e942b36acebe78e01129f81abfb2c432f40b","tid":1659114,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4faae859fc67c05a5ccc29c671e3f8bc11f682a","tid":1659114,"uid":228868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:48:10.000Z","msg":"講得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前幾日我都好沉迷睇果個法科post <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真唧牙膏式嘅神秘po真係好釣人癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會令人一直想追落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追po果幾日都無咩精神，所以放棄繼續追了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老實講死者已死我哋能力有限，加上學校又唔配合提供完整cctv<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警犬權力過大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我哋又無得fc真係好難搵得到真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哩啲要靠記者們嘅堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋不如暫時將集中力留返在生嘅受害者身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明佢地更需要我哋嘅關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb710552a84df0b4ae3859c4723c9fec12767fa5","tid":1659114,"uid":131713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc71b969196e63151a830620cac018c6434a2666","tid":1659114,"uid":294080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:33:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">希望大家花少少時間睇一睇：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1）中大吳同學企出嚟譴責黑警性暴力，同時踢爆有更多性暴力案件。<br />\n同晚，新屋嶺男義士喺tg題及被雞姦及輪姦。<br />\n<br />\n2）陳彥霖妹妹案件。教剪片嘅I大剪片剪得咁低質，合理嘛？播片日刻意將焦點擺喺部𨋢度、隔一日又出一堆片將焦點轉去替身度...明顯係有鋪排有計劃 ，目的係咩？<br />\n<br />\n3）法科救港。有另一個巴打講咗幾個法科post嘅套路我唔多講，我都唔排除入面嘅資訊係有用。不過希望大家留意一點，入面所題及嘅核彈，我哋係冇能力推得爆。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">簡單分析一下<br />\n1）黑警性暴力，有受害人出嚟指證，咁算唔算已fc？之前講咗好多日新屋嶺性暴力，主流意見都係話要fcfcfcfc！有兩個人鼓起哂勇氣喇，大家焦點去咗邊？<br />\n<br />\n2）陳彥霖案疑點太多，多到唔合理。係！好重要，要查案！不過查案目的係想揭露黑警惡行？性暴力案嘅爆炸性遠遠大過呢單案件。<br />\n我唔係冷血我都好唔開心。但對家更加知道15歲女童裸屍對我地嚟講都係好爆炸性。但老實講，黑警搭DI有心隱瞞我地根本唔會查到。<br />\n<br />\n3）法科想踢爆嘅陰謀更大，爆料節奏同DI差唔多，唧牙膏每日比少少你，目的就係引大家追，開到（5），係咪痴撚線？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n唔認同我講嘅嘢？<br />\n轉個角度諗一諗，大家都認同連登有好多人帶風向。咁呢幾日吹咩風？查案囉！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n但係黑警性暴力唔駛你查啊！<br />\n有受害人企出嚟喇！<br />\n15歲女童裸屍好值得大家關注！<br />\n女大學生比黑警帶入黑房搜身又點睇啊？<br />\n男中學生比黑警拘捕期間輪姦又點睇啊？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n本來都唔覺咁鬼，吹咗幾日查案風，今日岑子杰遇襲就更加證實到。啲時間節奏太巧合，一單就係巧合，幾單連續嚟就係陰謀喇！希望大家留意番：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警好撚驚我地追究性暴力</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:50:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17a2bfbb2349f1d4367e4266ed55c9d8c76f00d","tid":1659114,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:50:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e49f5f356103be388d9fc1219a980ace1ed77f9","tid":1659114,"uid":131713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d7763efaf29d449d0f9ae5aa4161b66d999add","tid":1659114,"uid":131713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:51:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad03fe418c5e766e77415f26d3bbceeebc970443","tid":1659114,"uid":131713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:52:33.000Z","msg":"吳同學個單黑警性暴力要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}